data.description: ***ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 2.75%***  Welcome to 865 Belmar Pass, Fairburn, GA 30213 – a stunning single-family home that seamlessly blends style, comfort, and functionality. This residence, built in 2012, offers a harmonious combination of modern features and timeless design.    Key Features:  Address: 865 Belmar Pass, Fairburn, GA 30213  Type: Single Family Home  Year Built: 2012  Bedrooms: 5  Bathrooms: 4.0  Full Basement  Heating: Heat Pump  Cooling: Central  Lot Size: 0.40 Acres  Interior Highlights:  Graciously appointed with 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. Full basement, partially finished. Home has TWO outdoor spaces, deck and patio.  Heating is efficiently handled by a modern heat pump, ensuring year-round comfort.  Central cooling to keep the interior ambient and refreshing.  Offering spacious and versatile living spaces.  A fireplace adds warmth and a cozy ambiance to the living area.  The exterior features other stylish elements that enhance the curb appeal.  The property sits on a generous lot spanning 0.40 acres, providing a balance of outdoor space and low maintenance.  Additional Property Information:    HOA dues contribute to the community's amenities and upkeep. Amenities include pool, playground, tennis courts, and clubhouse.    This single-family home follows a conventional architectural style, providing a timeless and classic aesthetic.  Constructed in 2012, the home reflects contemporary building standards.  The construction materials include a sturdy frame, ensuring durability and longevity.  Community and Location:    Situated in Fairburn, this home is part of a vibrant community with convenient access to local amenities.  The region offers a perfect balance of suburban tranquility and proximity to urban conveniences.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this impressive residence your new home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the charm of 865 Belmar Pass!
